{
  "stem": "7832.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And when I came home from school, I-- I was carrying the pot to the bakery, because that's where the oven was, and everybody's pot went into that oven for Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So all night long, it was cooking for Shabbat dinner.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And so that was done.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then-- and then I helped my grandmother and my mother prepare candle lighting and Shabbat services for Friday night.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And before it-- before candle light, I used to carry my father's and my grandfather's tallit to the-- to the temple, because they weren't allowed to carry.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I wasn't bat mitzvahed yet, so I was allowed to carry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So I did that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And when they come home-- when they came home from services, we had Shabbat dinner, and the traditional chicken soup, with the noodles in the soup, and chicken.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We didn't have too much chicken.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But it was-- it was delicious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And apple sauce from our own apples, our own apple trees.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And-- and it was just wonderful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And that was our Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My grandparents lived there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My grandparents lived in the same house, but they had their own-- it was a duplex.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So their entrance was on the other side.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we had a door from our house to go into our grandparents' house, through I think it was the kitchen and one of their rooms that connected.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we didn't have to go outside to go to their house, but we just went through from one house to the other.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And-- and our life, other than that, my grandfather was-- he kept us really busy, because he had a farm.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so on our home grounds, we had three cows, and we had a goat, and we had chickens, and geese.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
